1.title: Twitch Recap 2023
1.description: This user bled purple like it was their job, and was one of the most engaged members of Twitch in 2023!

message.body: I just spend a bunch of time optimizing a function in a program, the performance gain was unmeasurable :)
turns out I misread the performance trace and optimized the wrong function, the function I optimized isn't even called
yeah that is probably also going to be me, just need to find input that actually uses that function
but in other news, I got the program from ~65 seconds to 5 lol
It was doing a LOT of unnecessary parsing, re-compressing unchanged data and re-allocating data multiple times
I updated the node version which was basically a free performance gain, program was using v10, current latest is v21
